  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together the flax eggs, ferment-jang, red pepper flakes, sumac, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the lamb strips to the bowl and mix until they are fully coated with the marinade.",
    "Thread the lamb strips onto skewers and bake for 20 minutes, or until cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, toast the pita bread slices and slice into thin strips.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the yogurt and tomato sauce.",
    "To assemble the Iskender, place a few pieces of the lamb onto each pita bread strip, followed by a spoonful of the yogurt-tomato sauce mixture.",
    "Serve immediately in a bento-box.",
    "Garnish with additional sumac and red pepper flakes, if desired."
  ],
